{"tid":1825564,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【出錢又出力】馬浚偉自組製作團隊 目標5年拍10部社福電影","createTime":"2020-01-15T11:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T10:18:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":28,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f81afe6da4bb8da5ca6222edc3c2037a2b980d","tid":1825564,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"於製作電影《生前約死後》開始正式接觸電影行業，馬浚偉在開始中認識了影片製作、發行、配音、配樂及後期製作等精英，發現彼此理念相近，不會賺錢為主，而是希望幫助業界，馬浚偉於是牽頭聯同4個合作夥伴，組成戰略伙伴合作聯盟，今日更在土瓜灣舉行簽署儀式。<br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉指在港拍戲找投資者困難外，成本又高，票房也難以預計，希望透過這戰略伙伴合作聯盟，將製作成本減到最低，務求令業界從業員有工開，暫時定下目標是5年拍10部港產片，主要是社福電影，反映基層市民生活及面對困難。儀式上，馬浚偉即開聲邀請擔任司儀的林子博擔任新戲演員，更表明不只一部，子博感激之餘更自薦演舞台劇也可以。馬浚偉透露將於4月開拍一部以聾人為故事電影，他取材多個現實故事去編寫，他說：「我同樣會編、導、演，手頭仲有5個故事喺度，陸續會拍，但之後就唔會兼顧咁多崗位，但一定係我編寫。」<br />\n<br />\n為求降低成本，他將不收任何酬勞，也會成立自己攝影團隊去做，又會起用新人演出，使社福為題作品更有寫實感，這樣能令業界增加開拍電影機會，他笑言會從其他渠道演出賺錢過活，製作團隊也會接拍商業電影平衡收支，問到會否需要賣樓拍戲？他笑說：「暫時唔需要，我自己用積蓄去做，有需要先賣。」他透露聯盟中已有8位數字資金運作拍攝之用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zbzON8dGdaBvjEtmHp6fOURQxYA=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/MI33EZCEVPP5KNSGIKDRJRGBQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FzbzON8dGdaBvjEtmHp6fOURQxYA%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FMI33EZCEVPP5KNSGIKDRJRGBQM.jpg&h=767621f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200115/AJMQXPPGCAA6CFEDEGU7SPIWWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2FAJMQXPPGCAA6CFEDEGU7SPIWWM%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=3eb42c4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2FAJMQXPPGCAA6CFEDEGU7SPIWWM%2F&h=be07feb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200115/AJMQXPPGCAA6CFEDEGU7SPIWWM/</a>"},{"pid":"0d8674b021dbef9e24936046d2548dfca90f8dba","tid":1825564,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f52fa1c1895441391d2e98be61a012eed186b2e","tid":1825564,"uid":271516,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"好過班一線偽人多多聲"},{"pid":"b00ac9ebee9e136fdbd51004620e7f84c1cec10f","tid":1825564,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"香港ben affleck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94b77989abfaa1e95745191ddb164e39139f761","tid":1825564,"uid":76216,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:41:11.000Z","msg":"馬仔係真心膠黎"},{"pid":"a9358bc2353d7a01324c6f7c4027746bf1c6c148","tid":1825564,"uid":25797,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"之前都出錢幫過癌症女歌手出歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567114289342e94afa66b599920147c086c5ba7d","tid":1825564,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1b8fa4a572ff4ebf956fcd09296394819e3989","tid":1825564,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"佢之前果套比人屌到仆街"},{"pid":"68604854f4e99281367051c121d4d3b3a9aa078b","tid":1825564,"uid":173147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"細妹！家姐！"},{"pid":"bdb8d70244b4389f536e711786c951